22

00:01:26,100  -->  00:01:31,620
We want and need to close loops efficiently to prevent them from running indefinitely,

23

00:01:31,620  -->  00:01:33,640
which could lead to endless loops.

24

00:01:33,640  -->  00:01:38,040
Endless loops occur when the loops terminating condition is never met,

25

00:01:38,040  -->  00:01:42,830
